"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8717580-olden-goldie-mcevoy-may-swim-on-to-2032-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cam McEvoy is about to release his secrets, believing they can propel him to swim at his home Brisbane Olympics as a 38-year-old.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  McEvoy, aged 30, is Australia's oldest Olympic swimming gold medallist with his dazzling dash delivering victory in the men's 50m freestyle in Paris.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9993387035859799, \"rank\": 0.0006084267794681088, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999218835, \"rank\": 7.811425321251623e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His Friday night feat justifies McEvoy's gamble to re-write the training manual for the freestyle sprint.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Until the Paris Games, he'd kept most chapters closed, not wanting to offer his rivals insight to his revolutionary methods.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, he's an open book.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been inundated with questions and interest,\\\" McEvoy said.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think it will go a long way not only for athletes who are high performance but for the amount of ex-swimmers who quit when they are 16, 17, because they just did not like the kilometres or they had injuries.\\\"\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy took a hiatus from swimming after his third Olympics in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9894949269245891, \"rank\": 0.010551591517845196, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn't sure he'd return until he visited Paris in 2022 to attend the wedding of the sister of his girlfriend Maddie.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999218835, \"rank\": 7.811425321251623e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\", \"score\": 0.9383502493334585, \"rank\": 0.0657001484362414, \"text\": \"Maddie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They drove past the Paris La Defense Arena, built as the home stadium of rugby union club Racing 92 and transformed into Europe's largest indoor arena.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_\\u2013_Une_Ville_En_Concert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris La Defense\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_\\u2013_Une_Ville_En_Concert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_\\u2013_Une_Ville_En_Concert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy knew it was where a drop-in pool would be placed for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And he knew, at that drive-by moment, he wanted to swim again.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was the day that I went all in,\\\" McEvoy said.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All in meant ditching traditional training for the sprint freestyles which McEvoy experienced since his Olympic debut in London a dozen years ago.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999976221261, \"rank\": 2.374399046964915e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy is nicknamed The Professor - he studies phsyics and maths, wants to be an astronaut, and has previously raced with what most thought were sound waves emblazoned on his swim cap.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, they were gravitational waves in a nod to Einstein's general theory of relativity which, in part and in layman terms, covers the stretching and contraction of space-time.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.212746867594728e-13, \"text\": \"Einstein\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy returned to the pool, shunning age-old methods in favour of a new-age hunch: there was a better way.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always knew there was potentially another way to do things for sprint freestyle,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will do it.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it did not work, the closure is right there.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And if it worked, I could be better.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I can get closure coming back as well.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were training sessions where you second-guess it, you are in the pits and things are not feeling too great.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the amount of times that happened, it was 10-fold the amount of times where I thought 'this is special'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Endless kilometres staring at the black line on the bottom of a pool were replaced by rock climbing and calisthenics among other left-field activities.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard to explain the two-year process that it took to get here and the route I took,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That act of creation, effectively, over the last two years ... being the guinea pig and seeing where it would take me, is something that I am going to be most proud of.\\\"\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy released teasers about his training before Paris.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3262, \"end\": 3267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999218835, \"rank\": 7.811425321251623e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, he will detail the entire big bang.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And swimming at the Brisbane Olympics as a 38-year-old?\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the motivation is there and the body is holding up, I do not see why not,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Associated Press  Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also includes evening update.\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens  Do not miss updates on news about the Public Service.\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Catch up on the news of the day and unwind with great reading for your evening.\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Get the editor's insights: what's happening & why it matters.\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3891